name: Sunburn Music Festival
about: Sunburn is a commercial electronic dance music festival held in India. It is Asia's largest music festival. The festival is an amalgamation of Music, Entertainment, Food and Shopping, and was ranked by CNN in 2009 as one of the Top 10 Festivals in the world. Mayank Kataria is the major event promoter.
